      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those needing dependable daily transportation. The engine and transmission are in good working order, and the car starts consistently and drives well. While the mechanical components are sound, please note that the exterior shows some signs of age, including minor scratches and paint fading in a few spots. The interior is functional but exhibits typical wear and tear from regular use. This is a solid, honest car for anyone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that still has plenty of life left in it.",
