      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently maintained in showroom-grade condition. This vehicle represents the zenith of automotive care, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that meets the most exacting standards. For the collector or enthusiast seeking a turn-key investment, this vehicle offers an unrivaled opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering and aesthetics.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
