    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available now is a collector-grade A80 Supra Turbo, preserved in its original factory configuration. This example features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, utilizing its sequential twin-turbocharger setup to deliver linear power across the rev range. Mated to the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with crisp gear synchronization. The chassis retains its factory-specified rigidity, complemented by an untouched OEM suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every VIN tag is present, and the engine bay exhibits no signs of heat cycling or aftermarket intrusion. For the purist seeking mechanical integrity and peak performance, this is a turnkey investment.",
